sentence: The Home Depot, Inc. 's ( HD ) share price has entered into oversold territory with an RSI value of 21.3.
The Zacks Consensus Estimate for Home Depot for the full year period has remained flat over the past two months at $3.75 per share.
Currently, Home Depot has a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), suggesting that now might be a good time to get in on ( HD ) after its recent drop.
